{"tid":2059664,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"身為塞爾維亞人，愛（中）國是必須的！郝海東之子被塞爾維亞球會解僱","createTime":"2020-06-11T05:35:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T05:35:53.000Z","uid":48040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"47c7855c4cee25dff5b8ba66f8f7c0b52c7b6d73","tid":2059664,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T05:35:53.000Z","msg":"郝海東是前中國國腳，因發表反共言論遭到中國封殺。<br />\n近日，其子郝潤澤就被塞爾維亞尼球會Radnicki Nis解聘，而該球會聲稱與政治無關。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3hr4P2q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3hr4P2q&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjROSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=90f7f326\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3hr4P2q</a><br />\n<br />\n中國是塞爾維亞重要的政治及經濟盟友，中國向這一巴爾干國家提供了價值數十億美元的貸款，用於基礎設施建設。早前塞爾維亞支持國安法。<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-05-31/414744\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-05-31%2F414744&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjROSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=8a3ebdf6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-05-31/414744</a><br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n黃channel撐得好辛苦，可以幫手subscribe嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uff_OCto3EI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fuff_OCto3EI&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjROSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=0d9e0c85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uff_OCto3EI</a>"}]}